snippet.title: Elrentaros Wanderings Gameplay Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Elrentaros Wanderings Walkthrough

Let's Play - Elrentaros Wanderings

The protagonist visits Erlentaros, a town at the furthest end of Melvania, where they interact with its unique residents and set out on an adventure in search of what can be done for them. However, during their adventure, they awaken surrounded by light, and find themselves in a completely different world. Perhaps this is their true world?
